axisstyle           bar_var                 horizontal_notick // (default: horizontal_notick)

* Ticks
*******
tickposition        axis_tick               outside // (default: outside)
linewidth           tick                    thin // (default: thin)
gsize               tick                    vsmall // (default: tiny)

* Tick label
************
